# b3_arm_clip.shot — reproduce the rifle-arm-through-thin-solid bug.
#
# Player walks up to the col-55 wall (x=1760-1792, 5 tiles tall),
# aims past it (cursor on the far side), and the rifle arm reaches
# toward the cursor — straight into the wall. We expect the arm to
# either be pushed out by collision or stop at the wall surface;
# pre-fix it draws inside the tiles.

window 1280 720
seed   1 1
out    build/shots/b3
mouse  1100 360                 # cursor on the right; aim will be world-converted
contact_sheet sheet cols 4 cell 480 270

at  20 shot start

# Walk to the wall.
at  30 press right
burst walk from 80 to 320 every 40

# Should be against or near the wall by now. Hold the cursor over to
# the right (already set) so the rifle arm extends into/past the wall.
burst against from 330 to 380 every 5

at 420 end
